OL,3,CArsonist puts prison in lockdown after
OL,4,Cplanting 'joke' bomb
OL,6,FAn arsonist who burned down a
OL,7,FThorntons branch has put a prison in
OL,8,Flockdown after planting a hoax
OL,9,Fimprovised bomb.
OL,11,FMatthew Lea was jailed for 51 months
OL,12,Fat Crown Court in 2019 after he
OL,13,Ftorched Longton Thorntons, twice stole
OL,14,Ffrom Wrights pies, and pulled out a
OL,15,Fscrewdriver on a Royal University
OL,16,FHospital security guard.JThe 23-year-
OL,17,Fold was being held at Dovegate Prison,
OL,18,Fon the Staffordshire-Derbyshire border.
