OL,3,CArsonist puts prison in lockdown after
OL,4,Cplanting 'joke' bomb
OL,6,FHe was later moved to HMP Lowdham
OL,7,FGrange when the prison was forced into
OL,8,Flockdown.JLea had left a plastic
OL,9,Fbottle fitted with wires and white
OL,10,Fpowder under a door after he had
OL,11,Fcovered a CCTV camera lens with tissue
OL,12,Fpaper.
OL,14,FHe also had Isis and Taliban terrorist
OL,15,Fpropaganda.JLea has been jailed for 20
OL,16,Fmonths at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,17,Ffollowing the incident in 2022.JJudge
OL,18,FRosalind Coe KC said:
