OL,3,CArsonist puts prison in lockdown after
OL,4,Cplanting 'joke' bomb
OL,6,F"It was your actions which caused the
OL,7,Fsegregation unit to have to be
OL,8,Fevacuated and the police and bomb
OL,9,Fdisposal experts to have to be called
OL,10,Fout and caused a huge amount of
OL,11,Fdisruption to the prison.
OL,13,F"Whether it was a joke or otherwise,
OL,14,Fyou clearly intended for people to
OL,15,Fbelieve it might be an explosive
OL,16,Fdevice.
