OL,3,CArsonist puts prison in lockdown after
OL,4,Cplanting 'joke' bomb
OL,6,F"The SD card contained Isis propaganda
OL,7,Fand Taliban material and whether or
OL,8,Fnot you had a particular interest in
OL,9,Fradicalisation that the material
OL,10,Fcontained that is an aggravating
OL,11,Ffeature."JLea pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fpossessing a prohibited item inside
OL,13,Fprison and placing an article with
OL,14,Fintent to cause fear of violence. He
OL,15,Fhas 13 previous convictions for 34
OL,16,Foffences.JShahida Begum, mitigating,
OL,17,Fsaid her client disputes any interest
OL,18,Fin terrorism or radicalisation and
OL,19,Fhaving had a difficult upbringing,
OL,20,Fincluding physical abuse in foster
OL,21,Fcare, is vulnerable.JShe said: "He was
OL,22,Fvery, very silly and immature and when
OL,23,Fhe was spoken to by the prison staff
OL,24,Fhe told them it was a joke."
